- Components should use input/output isgnals instead of classic @Input() @Output()
- Components should use @If style syntax (and other control flow) instead of the classic *ngIf style directives.
- Components should always have their own html and scss file
- Use scss, not css files
- Components should follow strict material design guidelines.
- Don't use ng-deep.  It's deprecated.
- Make sure to use or update the approprate theme and global CSS.

